{"name": "lazyplot", "metadata": {"name": "lazyplot", "version": "0.1.7", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["matplotlib", "numpy", "pillow"], "summary": "plot matplotlib graph easily", "upload_time": 1733755538}, "documentation": ["# lazyplot\n\nModule for using matplotlib easily.\n\n## install\n```\npip install lazyplot\n```\n\n## usage\n### lazy_plot\nDraw graphs by entering only np.ndarray data.\n```\nfrom lazyplot import lazy_plot\nx = np.random.rand(3, 30)\nlazy_plot(x)\n\n# Simple customization\nlazy_plot(x, figure_config={\"figsize\"=(8,20), \"colmuns\"=2, \"plot_type_2d\"=\"plot\"})\n```\n\n### custom plot\nDraw more detailed graph by using user-specified LazyAxes\n```\nfrom lazyplot import LazyAxes, custom_plot\ndraw_info = LazyAxes(y=np.random.rand(2,30), title=\"random value\", plot_type=\"scatter\", color=\"blue\")\ncustom_plot(draw_info)\n```\n\n### FigureConfig\nFigreConfig can be overridden by giving a dictionary-type configuration item to the figure_config of lazy_plot and custom_plot.\n\n- figsize (tuple[int, int])figsize of matplotlib.Figure (default= (5, 4))\n- layout (\"tight\" | \"constrained\") : layout of matplotlib.Figure (default= \"constrained\")\n- linewidth (float) : linewidth of graph (default= 2.0)\n- columns (int) : number of columns in graph display.  (default= 1)\n    \n- plot_type_1d (\"plot\" | \"hist\" | \"bar\"): default plot type of 1 demensional array. (default= \"plot\")\n- plot_type_1d (\"plot\" | \"scatter\" | \"imshow\" | \"boxplot\"): default plot type of 2 demensional array. (default= \"imshow\")\n- plot_type_3d (\"scatter\"): default plot type of 3 demensional array. (default= \"scatter\")\n    \n- dpi (float) : dpi of matplotlib.Figure (default= 100)\n\n\n\n### LazyAxes\n\n- y (np.ndarray) \\*REQUIRED\n- plot_type (\"plot\" | \"hist\" | \"bar\" | \"scatter\" | \"imshow\" | \"boxplot\") \\*REQUIRED\n\n- title (str)\n- t (np.ndarray)\n- labels (list[str])\n- x_label (str)\n- y_label (str)\n- x_lim (tuple[float|None, float|None])\n- y_lim (tuple[float|None, float|None])\n- color (list[str | tuple[int, int, int]])\n- alpha (float)\n- line_style (list[str])\n- marker_style (list[str])\n- linewidth (float)\n- aspect (float | Literal[\"auto\"])\n- invert_xaxis (bool)\n- invert_yaxis (bool)"], "modules": [{"name": "lazyplot", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "lazyplot.custom_plot", "xref": {"fqname": "lazyplot.plot.custom_plot", "project": null}}, {"name": "lazyplot.lazy_plot", "xref": {"fqname": "lazyplot.plot.lazy_plot", "project": null}}, {"name": "lazyplot.LazyAxes", "xref": {"fqname": "lazyplot.config.LazyAxes", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "lazyplot.config", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "lazyplot.config.FIGURE_LAYOUT", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lazyplot.config.PLOT_TYPE_1D", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lazyplot.config.PLOT_TYPE_2D", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lazyplot.config.PLOT_TYPE_3D", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lazyplot.config.COLOR", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lazyplot.config.MARKER_STYLE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lazyplot.config.LINE_STYLE", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "lazyplot.config.FigureConfig", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "lazyplot.config.FigureConfig.__post_init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["validate after initialize--------------------------------"]}, {"name": "lazyplot.config.FigureConfig.validate", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["validate property----------------------------------------"]}, {"name": "lazyplot.config.FigureConfig.set_by_key", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": 